# 統一所有文字檔在 repo 與 working tree 皆為 LF,終結 autocrlf 的 LF/CRLF 警告
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows 批次檔必須是 CRLF 才能正確執行
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf

# 二進位檔案不做任何轉換
*.exe binary
*.zip binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.jar binary
*.gz binary
*.litematic binary
*.schematic binary
*.nbt binary
